node.text:
Is your dream suit so unique that only really you could design it? If so, we have a surprise for you! Introducing our D.I.Y. Swimsuit Kit. It comes with everything you need to sew your perfect suit from scratch. Sound crazy? It's easier than you'd think! Link in bio to find out more! 

#jolyn #diy #swimsuit

node.text: Harriet Brown is a World Champion Surf Ironwoman, Australian Team Captain, Ironwoman Series Champion and Molokai to Oahu Paddleboard Champion and record holder! As a surf Ironwoman she trains up to 16 sessions, six days per week across a combination of disciplines including; board, swim, ski, run and gym. "It's tiring but so much fun! I love being at the beach and appreciate that I have had the opportunity to race all over the world and my sport has taken me to some incredible locations." Harriet also works as an Exercise Physiologist, Hydration Specialist and Coach. "So much of what I do is centered around sports performance and living an active and healthy life."Harriet is not only an amazing athelte but speaks to and mentors young women about self-confidence, body confidence and female athlete health. @harrietbrown is definitely a Woman Who Inspires Us! #jolyn
